snippet.title: Zen Bound 2 - Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available May 24th as a digital download on the Nintendo Switch!
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/zen-bound-2-switch

A unique award-winning tactile down-tempo puzzle game from Secret Exit.

Featuring:
* Tactile gyro-controlled object-wrapping gameplay
* Over 100 levels
* 5.1 surround soundtrack by Ghost Monkey
